<h2 id="expressions">Expressions</h2>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>But with such a father and mother, and such <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="low connections"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(低贱的亲戚)</code></b>, I am afraid there is no chance of it.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>I am inclined to think that you would not wish to see your sister <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="make such an exhibition"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(出这种洋相)</code></b>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>To this speech Bingley made no answer, but his sisters <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="gave it their hearty assent"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(对此表示衷心赞成)</code></b>, and <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="indulged their mirth"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(寻开心)</code></b> for some time <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="at the expense of"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________([意译]拿着.../在牺牲...的情况下)</code></b> their dear friend’s vulgar relations.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Elizabeth assured him that she could <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="suit herself"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(随自己的意愿/觉得满足)</code></b> perfectly with those in the room.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Your <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="picture"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(描述)</code></b> may be very exact, but this <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="was all lost upon me"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(我完全没有注意/理解)</code></b>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>She was still very <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="poorly"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(病得厉害)</code></b>, and Elizabeth would not <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="quit her"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(离开她)</code></b> at all, till late in the evening, when she <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="had the comfort of (doing something)"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(做某事后才放下心来)</code></b> seeing her asleep.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>I could hardly <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="keep the countenance"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(不笑出来)</code></b>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>But suspecting them to be <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="playing high"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(豪赌)</code></b>, she declined it, and making her sister the excuse, said she would amuse herself, for the short time she could stay below with a book.</p>
  </li>
</ol>
